{"tid":1977694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"個制從來都唔存在，獨立先係出路","createTime":"2020-04-18T07:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T03:49:29.000Z","uid":79589,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de5c30056678fad920310f649d0c16fb4537b56c","tid":1977694,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"個問題已經唔係個制度，因為個制從來都冇出現過<br />\n<br />\n三權分立要成功係要有真民主政制，香港從來都冇有過民主。<br />\n<br />\n以前冇問題係因為官仲見得下人，做到啲野，但由始至終都係人治。<br />\n<br />\n共匪一日存在，香港一日都唔會有民主，因為最大權力永遠都係共匪手上。<br />\n<br />\n冇力量嘅正義係無能，無權力嘅議員只係擺設<br />\n<br />\n立法會、功能組別可以進攻<br />\n<br />\n但重點係要比全世界知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港，要獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"e98a004174850e1c4122f8ccece4a9082a0dcb99","tid":1977694,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0ad2cb0f889352d4a6e84536780aec5657c2d9f","tid":1977694,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"癈話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97119d31d926e60d0c1cbdd76d9b7d83521747e3","tid":1977694,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0ad2cb0f889352d4a6e84536780aec5657c2d9f","tid":1977694,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"癈話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"要將廢話變成人人都識講"},{"pid":"9114cbe2444bda262eb1bc2a3e911c5dfb85cda0","tid":1977694,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97119d31d926e60d0c1cbdd76d9b7d83521747e3","tid":1977694,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0ad2cb0f889352d4a6e84536780aec5657c2d9f","tid":1977694,"uid":300785,"lik